race.comment: ZOU SENSATION (4) was brave in winning the Listed Weekend Hustler over this distance at Caulfield last start where he took charge early, opened a big gap and held them off. Kept up to the mark with a trial since. Draws well and maps to get every chance. MEDIA WORLD (3) was okay behind Private Eye in the G3 Moonga Stakes last time out. He was well backed to win here prior and should get a good run on speed. The consistent WARNIE (6) was second in the Moonga albeit no match for the winner and should be right there again. PAYLINE (2) and STEPARTY (1) are both building in fitness. Expect them to hit their peaks today.
